65fc671d4b57cfabf2bdefbf3717276a9c75c908.query:
insert into replies (handler, pattern, template, channel, to_mention, enabled, created_by) values
            ("Npc", "^!twitter$", $3, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!(?:youtube|yt)$", $4, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!clips$", $5, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!vod(?:s)?(?:-)?(?:channel)?(?:s)?$", $6, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!reddit$", "reddit.com/r/PedroPeepos", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!discord$", $7, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!instagram$", $8, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!tiktok$", $9, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!social(?:s)?$", $10, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", $12, "Yep Caedrel should be streaming some solo Q today. Follow twitter.com/caedrelupdates for more updates ok", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", $11, "Caedrel will cast G2 vs MAD (Friday 21th April) & BDS series (Sunday 23th April) You can find LEC schedule here lolesports.com/schedule?leagues=lec", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!end(?:ing)?(?:-)?song$", "okaywill - Chicken Dinner: youtube.com/watch?v=B_rAI7zaVZU", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!emote(?:s)?$", "To see emotes install 7TV 7tv.app. These are Caedrel's emotes: 7tv.app/users/61e2b8461f8f9d5cf63321a1", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!(?:prime(?:(?:-)?sub(?:s)?)?|sub(?:s(?:cribe)?)?)$", "You can sub to Caedrel's channel and use your Twitch Prime here twitch.tv/subs/caedrel", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!delay$", "YEP stream has 25s delay", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("Npc", "^!(?:playlist|listen(?:ing)?|song(?:s)?)$", "Don't belive Moobot KEKW the song we're listening should be in this playlist https://open.spotify.com/playlist/0fapwQkpLm6pLE5wzDL31v?si=d5ba5b6c44e6430a", $2, 0, 1, $1),

            ("Npc", "^!time$", "It's {{ now('Europe/Berlin')|format_date_time('%I:%M %p') }} in Caedrel's timezone", $2, 0, 1, $1),

            ("Gamba", "^!gamba$", "", $2, 0, 1, $1),

            ("Npc", ".*(?:\s+)?(?:caedALLO|peepoSitHey|good\s+morning)(:?\s+)?.*", "caedALLO", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            ("Npc", ".*(?:\s+)?(?:thanks|thank\s+you|thnx|ty)(?:\s+)?.*$", "ok", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            ("Npc", ".*(?:\s+)?(?:GIGACHAD|best\s+mod|good\s+mod|PETTHEMODS|<3|heart|love)(?:\s+)?.*", "widexddL", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            ("Npc", ".*(?:\s+)?(?:bye)(?:\s+)?.*", "bye", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            ("Npc", ".*(?:\s+)?(?:Pog|PogU|POGGIES|POGGERS|caedPog)(?:\s+)?.*", "xddFlush", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            ("Npc", ".*(?:\s+)?(?:xdd.*)(?:\s+)?.*", "widexddL", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            ("Npc", ".*(?:\s+)?(?:Aware|TrollAware|TrollDespair|Despairge|xddDespair)(?:\s+)?.*", "Aware Despairge", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            ("Npc", ".*(?:\s+)?(?:DonoWall)(?:\s+)?.*", "classic DonoWall Despair", $2, 1, 0, $1);

8777267122998ba725c23f3c489ffe3d234606a6.query:
select
                    id,
                    handler as "handler: Handler",
                    pattern,
                    case_insensitive,
                    template,
                    to_mention,
                    channel,
                    enabled,
                    created_by,
                    created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                    updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
                from replies
                where enabled = 1 and (channel is null or channel = $1) and (handler is null or handler = $2)
                order by id asc
